trans-unit.source: Enables you to create, configure, and access the properties of a workflow service.
trans-unit.target: Kan du oppretter, konfigurerer og få tilgang til egenskaper for en arbeidsflyt-tjeneste.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.WorkflowService"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.WorkflowService"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether the workflow service has buffered receive processing enabled for incoming messages.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om Arbeidsflyttjenesten er bufret motta behandling aktivert for innkommende meldinger.

trans-unit.source: The buffered receive feature enables a workflow service to process out-of-order messages without relying on complicated poison message handling.
trans-unit.target: Bufret receive-funksjonen aktiverer en arbeidsflyt-tjeneste for å behandle feil rekkefølge meldinger uten avhengige kompliserte giftmeldinger.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the workflow service has buffered receive processing enabled for incoming messages; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis Arbeidsflyttjenesten er bufret motta behandling aktivert for innkommende meldinger. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Verifies that a workflow service is correctly configured according to the validation logic.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollerer at en Arbeidsflyttjenesten er riktig konfigurert i henhold til logikken validering.
